# Meister DEV ProPR — AI reviewer exclusion patterns
# Syntax: one glob pattern per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# NOTE: providing this file overrides the built-in defaults, so the
# standard EF Core generated-file patterns are repeated here explicitly.

# ── EF Core auto-generated files ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Migration designer snapshots and model snapshots are 100% tool-generated.
# They reflect migrations and schema changes that are reviewed on the .cs files.
**/Migrations/*.Designer.cs
**/Migrations/*ModelSnapshot.cs

# ── OpenAPI / generated client ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# openapi.json is the generated API contract artifact at the repo root.
# The TypeScript client under generated/ is produced from openapi.json.
# Keep these diffs excluded from AI review to avoid spending review budget on
# mechanical contract/client regeneration, even though API behavior changes must
# still keep the contract aligned.
openapi.json
admin-ui/src/services/generated/**

# --- ProRV Text Assets ---
src/MeisterProPR.ProRV/Assets/*.txt
